        <h3>Our Mission</h3>
        <p>At BellyFull, our mission is simple but powerful: to ensure that no one in our community goes hungry. We believe that access to nutritious food is a basic human right, and we are committed to connecting those who care with those in need.</p>

        <p><strong>We work to:</strong></p>
        
        <p><strong>1. Bridge the Gap:</strong> Connect individuals, restaurants, and organizations with surplus food to families and individuals facing food insecurity.</p>
        
        <p><strong>2. Reduce Food Waste:</strong> Transform food that would otherwise go to waste into meaningful meals for those who need them most.</p>
        
        <p><strong>3. Build Community:</strong> Foster a spirit of sharing and mutual support within our neighborhoods and cities.</p>
        
        <p><strong>4. Educate and Empower:</strong> Raise awareness about hunger and food waste while empowering individuals to make a positive impact.</p>
        
        <p><strong>5. Create Sustainable Solutions:</strong> Develop long-term, scalable approaches to food security that can be replicated in communities worldwide.</p>
        
        <p>Through our platform, we make it easy for good-hearted people to share resources and create a network of care that ensures no meal goes to waste and no one goes hungry.</p>
        
